not a smiley face.

07:59.252 --> 08:00.652
Charming.

08:00.653 --> 08:03.272
Um, listen, I need to talk
to you about something.

08:03.273 --> 08:05.023
Yeah, sure. What's up?

08:06.126 --> 08:07.659
Oh, you bad girl.

08:07.660 --> 08:10.095
You know that money
you gave to me

08:10.096 --> 08:11.397
to invest in my business?

08:11.398 --> 08:12.564
Yeah, what about it?

08:12.565 --> 08:14.233
Well, here's the thing.

08:14.234 --> 08:16.878
I-I know I said I was going
to buy advertising...

08:16.890 --> 08:18.169
Oh, I almost forgot.

08:18.202 --> 08:19.846
I told Rose about how well
you're doing for me,

08:19.872 --> 08:21.123
and now she wants in.

08:21.124 --> 08:22.408
She does?

08:22.409 --> 08:24.676
Oh, yeah.
And she's loaded, too.

08:24.677 --> 08:26.111
Huh.

08:26.112 --> 08:27.846
So what did you
want to talk about?

08:27.847 --> 08:30.749
Uh...

08:33.852 --> 08:36.321
Just that we're making
money up the wazoo.

08:37.222 --> 08:39.124
So you're going to need
a bigger wazoo.

08:39.125 --> 08:41.092
That's great.

08:43.996 --> 08:47.166
