an exception here.

09:30.844 --> 09:32.544
You're welcome.

09:32.545 --> 09:35.814
Can you wire the money
over today?

09:35.815 --> 09:38.066
I can give it
to you right now.

09:39.035 --> 09:40.686
Whoa!

09:40.687 --> 09:42.754
You surprised me.

09:42.755 --> 09:44.923
Oh, Alan, Alan, Alan.

09:44.924 --> 09:46.391
What are you doing?

09:46.392 --> 09:47.859
Oh, what do you mean?

09:47.860 --> 09:49.895
I'm-I'm just taking a break
between patients.

09:50.897 --> 09:52.965
Oh, uh, uh...

09:52.966 --> 09:55.701
Chiropractic X-ray glasses.

09:57.036 --> 10:00.005
Cutting-edge stuff.

10:00.006 --> 10:01.139
Oh, please.

10:01.140 --> 10:02.674
There's nobody
in the waiting room.

10:02.675 --> 10:04.276
