a receptionist.

10:04.277 --> 10:06.411
Oh, she's off.
It's a Jewish holiday.

10:06.412 --> 10:07.913
Which one?

10:07.914 --> 10:11.717
Hava-na-kuchnik.

10:13.586 --> 10:14.820
What are you doing here?

10:14.821 --> 10:16.889
Did you really think
I was going to invest

10:16.890 --> 10:18.290
without doing my due diligence?

10:18.291 --> 10:20.425
