10:20.426 --> 10:22.528
Now I know
what's really going on.

10:22.529 --> 10:23.562
No, you don't.

10:23.563 --> 10:25.564
You're stealing from
your own family.

10:25.565 --> 10:29.067
Oh... I guess you do.

10:29.903 --> 10:32.120
