11:30.396 --> 11:32.998
Winner, winner, chicken dinner.

11:32.999 --> 11:35.434
She tells on me, I tell on her.

11:35.435 --> 11:37.603
Criss-cross, apple sauce.

11:37.604 --> 11:40.238
I got nothing to worry about.

11:40.239 --> 11:43.342
Herky-jerky,
where's your turkey?

11:43.343 --> 11:45.410
Why do you keep
talking like that?

11:45.411 --> 11:46.945
I'm looking for a catch phrase.

11:46.946 --> 11:48.547
Zippy?

11:48.548 --> 11:52.084
Flim-flam, you're in a jam.

11:54.704 --> 11:56.321
Oh, hey!

11:56.322 --> 11:57.839
Somebody in
there with you?

11:57.840 --> 11:58.990
Oh, no, no.

11:58.991 --> 12:00.659
Um, how can I help you?

12:00.660 --> 12:02.494
Just brought
your clean towels.

12:02.495 --> 12:03.862
Oh, uh, what about
my washcloths?

12:03.863 --> 12:04.963
