when we got married.

12:39.332 --> 12:40.499
Uh-oh.

12:40.500 --> 12:41.700
Shh.

12:42.535 --> 12:44.169
Who is it?

12:44.170 --> 12:45.537
It's Alan.

12:45.538 --> 12:47.005
We need to talk.

12:47.006 --> 12:49.207
Just a second.

12:51.944 --> 12:53.011
Let's go, Rose.

12:53.012 --> 12:54.429
